description:
Hey! Looking for the quickest food delivery? That’s easy with our new talabat app.

Whether you want a pizza, burger or groceries, choose from thousands of markets and restaurants in your city and put your hunger to an end. We’ve got it all – fast delivery, unlimited options, easy online payment and vouchers all at your fingertips.

Order your favorite food and get it delivered to wherever you are, but also get your groceries delivered to you with more cities to come. Your needs, done - simply download our app, choose your food or groceries and pay in a few taps via card or cash upon delivery. 

Browse a multitude of restaurant menus and order from countless stores. With our filters and smart search functions, you can find the exact menu or product you want in no time, available to personalize at your request.

"Pay online or in cash"
Add info to your account on our new talabat app to speed up your order process. Pay in cash or save card details to pay online, reorder your favorites anytime and save addresses so you’re ready for delivery wherever you are. Like planning ahead? Pick what time you want us to deliver to avoid hunger kicking in.

"Track your order from start to finish"
That’s right; follow your delivery from the moment it’s confirmed to the second we hand it to you. With notifications, you'll always be updated and our help center will answer any questions about your delivery – we’ve got you.

"Find exclusive deals"
Downloading the talabat app makes you a part of our fam. We’re more than food delivery; discover vouchers, promotions and deals and treat yourself to that midweek pizza or Friday night burger more often. By opting in for notifications, we'll also share new restaurants, supermarkets and stores in your area, so you’ll never miss out on the latest offers again.

Find us in Kuwait, the United Arab Emirates, Bahrain, Oman, Qatar, Jordan, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and Egypt.

Happy ordering.

Welcome to Planet Donuts, your ultimate destination in Jordan for an extraordinary journey through a galaxy of sweetness and delight. Our mission at Planet Donuts is not just to serve you a treat but to transport you to a world where every bite is an adventure, every flavor tells a story, and every visit is a cherished memory.

At the heart of Planet Donuts lies our passion for crafting the perfect donut - soft, fluffy, and bursting with flavors that are out of this world. Our menu is a constellation of handcrafted donuts, each one a masterpiece of taste and artistry. From the classic sugared and glazed varieties to innovative creations that push the boundaries of culinary imagination, there's a donut for every palate and occasion.

But our journey through the cosmos of confectionery doesn't stop at donuts. Planet Donuts is a haven for all things sweet, offering an eclectic assortment of cakes, ice creams, and refreshing drinks. Whether you're in the mood for a decadent chocolate cake, a scoop of rich, creamy ice cream, or a refreshing cold beverage, our menu is designed to satisfy your cravings and uplift your spirit.

Understanding the diverse tastes of our cosmic adventurers, we take pride in offering options that cater to everyone. Our menu includes vegan, gluten-free, and nut-free options, ensuring that everyone can enjoy the delights of Planet Donuts, regardless of dietary restrictions or preferences.

At Planet Donuts, we believe in the power of community and the magic of sharing joy. Our cozy, welcoming spaces are designed to be your go-to spot for casual meet-ups, celebrations, or a quiet moment of indulgence. With free Wi-Fi, comfortable seating, and a friendly atmosphere, we invite you to make Planet Donuts your second home.

Sustainability and responsibility towards our planet are at the core of our operations. We are committed to eco-friendly practices, from sourcing ingredients locally to minimize our carbon footprint, to using biodegradable packaging, ensuring that our love for sweets goes hand in hand with love for the Earth.

For those on the go, our efficient online ordering system and delivery service ensure that you can enjoy the delights of Planet Donuts from the comfort of your home or office. Our easy-to-navigate website and mobile app make ordering a breeze, bringing the universe of flavors right to your doorstep.

Join us at Planet Donuts for a journey like no other. Indulge in the ultimate sweet experience, where every visit is a voyage across a delicious galaxy. Follow us on social media for the latest updates, special offers, and a peek into the exciting world of Planet Donuts. Your adventure awaits!

Find a branch near you: easily find the nearest Al Ameed Coffee branch, view operating hours, and get directions with just a tap.
Stay informed: be the first to hear about special offers, exciting announcements, and new app features through our notification center.

Download the Al Ameed app today and elevate your coffee experience!

HungerStation – The First and Biggest Delivery App in Saudi Arabia

Whatever you need, HungerStation delivers it to you before anyone else. From your favorite restaurants, groceries, and pharmacies, to gifts and flowers. Our coverage reaches over 102 cities and regions across the Kingdom, with more than 55,000 restaurants and stores ready to serve you anytime.

Why HungerStation?
Because we’re the largest in Saudi Arabia: more than 55,000 restaurants and stores at your fingertips.

Variety that matches your cravings: whether it’s Pizza, Shawarma, Sushi, Sandwiches, Fresh Salad, Fast Food, Ice Cream, Coffee, Bakery treats, Japanese dishes, or authentic Arabic meals, you’ll always find what you’re looking for. Plus, you can enjoy international cuisines, traditional favorites, healthy options, organic products, and more.

Not just restaurants!

HungerStation Market: groceries, fresh fruits and vegetables, and cleaning products.

Pharmacies: from medicine to daily personal care.

Flowers & Gifts: want to surprise someone? Order now and we’ll deliver their gift wherever they are.

Payment your way: cash, card, or Apple Pay.

Daily deals & discounts tailored for you.

HungerStation Plus: unlimited free delivery from over 35,000 restaurants, stores, and pharmacies.

How to order? Just 4 easy steps:
1- Download the HungerStation app and set your location.
2- Choose a restaurant or store you like.
3- Browse the menu and add your favorites to the cart.
4- Order and relax, your order is on the way.

What makes us stand out?
Track your order step by step until it arrives.
Smart filters and search help you find the best restaurants and deals.
Real customer reviews to guide your choice.
24/7 customer support.
Schedule your order and get it delivered at the time that suits you.

New to HungerStation?
Enjoy a full year of unlimited free delivery from over 35,000 restaurants and stores as soon as you sign up.

HungerStation is more than just an app! It’s your shortcut to saving time and effort. Order in a few taps and rest assured, everything will arrive quickly and with quality.

Download HungerStation now.


HungerStation Before Everyone.

نقدم لزبائننا هذا التطبيق المميز ليزيد من متعة التسوق في جميع فروعنا.
تطبيق ذا كيك شوب يحتوي على مجموعه من الخصائص الرائعه التي تربط زبائننا مع علامتنا التجارية بطريقه بسيطة وسهلة, حيث يتيح لك الفرصة لتجميع النقاط مقابل كل عملية شرائية تقوم بها، إضافة للحصول على العديد من الهدايا وخاصة  في مناسباتك المميزة, لا داعي بعد اليوم لحمل اي بطاقه بلاستيكية  في محفظتك! اطلع على مجموع نقاطك التى يمكنك لاحقا استبدالها بالعديد من الجوائز وتابع جميع العروض الخاصة بنا عبر التطبيق. 

باعتبارك أحد زبائننا المميزين , يمكنك وبكل سهولة انشاء حسابك الخاص على التطبيق لتتعرف اكثر على منتجاتنا، مشاركتها مع اصدقاءك، و تحديد مواقع متاجرنا بكل بساطة و يسر والحصول على العديد من الهدايا و الجوائز فور قيامك بأي عمليه شرائية او عند مشاركة  هذا التطبيق مع اصدقاءك،  كما يتيح لك مشاركتنا  تجربتك مع ذا كيك شوب. 

عروض مميزة , اشعارات ومعرض للصور  يحتوي على العديد من صور الكيك  الشهيه وقائمة الطعام الخاصة بنا، كن على اطلاع مستمر لجميع منتجاتنا. 

تسوق اكثر و عزز تجربتك لتحصل على العديد من الامتيازات مع تطبيق برنامج الولاء الخاص بكيك شوب...

Forsa is the smarter way to save money, enjoy great food, and support sustainability. Partnering with restaurants, cafés, and bakeries, Forsa helps reduce food waste by offering surplus meals in surprise bags or custom packages at discounted prices.

With Forsa, you can:
• Save money by accessing meals at a fraction of the cost.
• Discover new places and try different cuisines around you.
• Support local businesses by purchasing their surplus food.
• Make a positive environmental impact by reducing food waste.
• Enjoy convenience with real-time offers, secure in-app payments, and location-based search.

Forsa isn’t just about affordable meals; it’s about being part of a community that values food, sustainability, and smart choices. Whether you’re seeking a budget-friendly option or want to support a greener future, Forsa makes it simple and rewarding.

Download Forsa today and turn every meal into an opportunity.
